&lt;div class="tip-box"&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Pro tip:&lt;/strong&gt; Build your bus with &lt;strong&gt;space between lanes&lt;/strong&gt;. You need room for underground belts to cross lanes and for inserters to pull items off the bus.
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-build-it"&gt;How to Build It&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="step-1-clear-a-large-area"&gt;Step 1: Clear a Large Area&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You need at least &lt;strong&gt;200 tiles wide&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;unlimited depth&lt;/strong&gt;. The bus grows as you research more technologies.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>